    What we do

    We’re the Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency (DVLA), holding more than 52 million driver records and more than 46 million vehicle records. We collect over £7 billion a year in Vehicle Excise Duty (VED).

    DVLA is an executive agency, sponsored by the Department for Transport.

    Read more about what we do
